<img src="https://biz-file.com/c/1905/498339-625x391.jpg" alt="Jewel 'shines bright like a diamond'" width="625" height="391">Jewel wax polish has been a firm favourite for South Africans ever since it was first introduced. For the launch of its new range of cleaning products, Amka turned to Just Design Jhb to help carry the trusted protection and cleaning associated with the brand beyond the floor and stoep, and into the house. The challenge for the Just Design team was how to cut through the visual clutter of an already noisy category. The solution: ‘simplicity’. A clean sophisticated approach that creates a sense of calm reassurance in a shelf full off flashes, claims and swooshes.The design heroes both the fresh modern scents used within the range, and the products’ usage and efficacy through ingredient imagery and visuals of beautifully shined tiles and sparkling plates. The Jewel ‘Diamond’ was also given a lift with the use of foiling, giving it depth and detail along with a more premium feel that is reflected throughout the rest of the label. <img src="https://biz-file.com/c/1905/498342-625x184.jpg" alt="Jewel 'shines bright like a diamond'" width="625" height="184">Despite being new to the market, the range has already put a sparkle in the eye of the consumer, winning Neilson’s ‘Product of the Year Award’ in the Home Care Category. This consumer-voted award is based on an independent survey of over 4,000 South African households for product innovation. Jewel, beautiful eye-catching design and innovation.Want to read about insights, trends and other cool stuff? Sign up to our mailing list.About Just DesignFor 20 years, Just Design has proven time and again that good thinking leads to great creative. With a national footprint and accounts across Africa, Middle East and Europe, they are the strategic design and innovation partners for many blue-chip clients and global brands, and are one of South Africa’s leading Innovation, Strategy and Design agencies.About JewelJewel is an affordable, everyday range of multi-purpose cleaning products. The range includes FloorGo Triple Wax Floor Polish (in Lavender, Red and Potpourri), WoodGlo Furniture Oil, Dishwashing Liquid (in Lime & Basil and Pomegranate & Berry), Tile Cleaner (in Lavender & Mint and Water Lily & Cucumber) and Laminate Floor Cleaner (in Almond & Honeysuckle). For more information, visit http://www.amka.co.za/project/jewel/. For further information, please contact:Vanessa Bosmanvanessa@justdesign.co.zabRev('brev-f447708b-a11f-44e5-b8e1-1402d2b12c82', '>a/\<az.oc.ngisedtsuj@assenav>"az.oc.ngisedtsuj;46#&assenav:otliam"=ferh "knalb_"=tegrat a<')+27 (0) 11 234 4249